deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Wednesday, February 21 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35. Order within 15 hrs 51 mins
features: 【Super Versatile Corner Shelf】 Without taking too much room, the 3 Tier storage shelf is perfect for kitchen counter, bathroom, living room, corner sink, office desk, countertop, dresser, coffee/tea corner bar, dessert bar and any places in your home. It can not only save space, but also a nice decoration.

【High Quality & Sturdy】 The over sink shelf is made of bamboo wood, which is easy to clean and stable on the countertop. Tube legs with 5 plastic non-slip feet, allow the shelf to stand firmly on the table and prevent items from falling.

【Spacious Space to Store】Three Shelves keep your items organized, allowing more surface area in a small space. You can use the shelf to augment your spice rack, holding many items including plants, lotions, makeups, books, office supplies, coffee items, tea cups, etc.
【Easy to Assemble】 Comes with clear instruction, only take few minutes to assembly. It is a easily tighten design for attaching shelves. Carefully tighten the hook with the small screwdriver.

【Flexible Use】The first and second shelves can be adjusted at various angles, meeting your stuff or space needs. You can put it straight across or in a corner against walls, it can also stand by itself as a table storage organization.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I wanted
reviews.reviewText: I looked all over in the local stores for the perfect shelf for the corner of the bathroom vanity and this was the perfect fit!! Easy to assemble with few parts.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adds a nice touch
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together. Directions are simple. I originally got this for my bathroom but was off by half an inch so now its in my kitchen. Which works out better for me cos my coffee maker fits under it and I can put all my coffee and spice supplies around it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really like this. Sturdy, perfect for my little corner in kitchen

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little shelf
reviews.reviewText: I wanted something to help organize the corner of my kitchen counter which is too small for my needs. This works great. It fit, was very easy to put together, and very nice for the price. It added much needed space, and looks great where it is at.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Space Saver and Looks!
reviews.reviewText: Super easy to assemble, looks great, holds a ton of items! If your sink area is small and super busy, this is a perfect investment and has Hooks to hang all you need! 10/10 recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 19, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very flimsy and too expensive for what it is
reviews.reviewText: This is a very wobbly and light-weight set of platforms. It looks and feels cheap, so for the price, I wasn't happy. It works OK and serves the purpose of enabling more things to be stacked on my bathroom shelf, but it doesn't look very good. At least it was easy to assemble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Counter space in my bathroom now!!
reviews.reviewText: I like everything about it. It was a snap to put together IF you follow the instructions…put it together upside down then you don’t have to worry about having a third arm to hold it. It’s perfect, another great Amazon purchase.UPDATE: For those of you that want to use it in the bathroom and barely have enough room around the sink for it to sit on…I just put a very small dab of hot glue on the legs that are perched precariously on the edges of the sink and they aren’t goin’ anywhere. Now they are even more perfect!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks nice, but pain to put together.
reviews.reviewText: This thing looks just like the picture, and is fairly nice esp for the price. Unfortunately, it only really works for a right sided corner or it kinda looks funny. The main complaint is that it was a pain in the butt to put together. It required a husband's help as it came in many pieces that required many steps. Otherwise, I love it. Amazon suggests I mention its sturdiness or ease to clean. Its a little wobbly so I wouldn't recommend it for a spice rack that will hold lots of small things you will be shuffling often. And its pretty easy to clean cuz im short and its a shelf that i can reach.
